data.description: Don't miss this amazing opportunity to own this stunning home in Sage Creek Subdivision! This home has it all: 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, hardwood floors on the main level, fresh paint and modern light fixtures! Enjoy the warmth of the gas fireplace in the living room or host a dinner party in the elegant dining room with coffered ceilings and arched doorways! The kitchen is a chef's dream, with an island, recessed lighting, custom pantry shelving, granite countertops and a new countertop range. There is also a guest suite on the main level with a full bath. The owner's suite upstairs is a retreat, with vaulted ceilings, double vanities, soaking tub and a huge walk-in closet. The other 4 bedrooms upstairs are spacious and have walk-in closets and ceiling fans as well. There are two full bathrooms upstairs, one shared and one private. The back yard is perfect for relaxing or entertaining, with a covered patio and a large, level, fenced-in area. There is also a storage building for extra space. The home has a double car garage and is conveniently located near I20, Bridgestone & more!
